content:
Score and rank ALL these items from FIVE sources. Apply STRICT FRESHNESS: keep ONLY items published ON OR AFTER ${cycle.dates.from} (last 72h). Return up to 10 as JSON array.

Cutoff (ISO): ${cycle.dates.from}
Now (ISO): ${cycle.dates.now}

=== NEWS (${cycle.dates.from} to ${cycle.dates.now}) ===
${cycle.fresh.news}

=== REDDIT DISCUSSIONS (created_utc available) ===
${cycle.fresh.reddit}

=== ARXIV PAPERS (published/updated dates available) ===
${cycle.fresh.arxiv}

=== PAPERS WITH CODE (extract recent paper dates if present) ===
${cycle.fresh.pwc}

=== SONAR REAL-TIME SEARCH (ensure last 72h) ===
${cycle.fresh.sonar}

Rules:
- Use date fields like published_at, date, created_utc, published, updated. If ambiguous or older than cutoff, discard.
- Prefer diversity across sources.
- Return ONLY JSON.
